data.description: MAJOR PRICE IMPROVEMENT!! Stop and check out this home now! This delightful brick residence in Hinesville, GA, is boasting with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a generous 1,513 sqft, this charming property sits on a peaceful cul-de-sac with a .25-acre lot. Step onto the open porch for morning coffee, and enjoy the spacious, fenced backyard - ideal for outdoor activities. Inside, the living space exudes warmth with a cozy fireplace, perfect for chilly evenings.  This home offers versatile living with a formal living room, a formal dining room, family room and an eat in breakfast area. The kitchen features modern convenience with stainless steel appliances, adding a touch of sophistication to daily living. Located just 5 minutes from Fort Stewart, this home strikes the perfect balance between tranquility and proximity. Embrace a lifestyle of comfort in this cozy gem.
